# RQ-53-10-01-150: Visual Inspection Daily

## Requirement Statement
The nose cone shall be visually inspectable for damage during daily pre-flight walk-around.

## Rationale
Early detection of impact damage, delamination, or surface defects.

## Acceptance Criteria
- All external surfaces visible from ground
- Access ladder/platform not required for inspection
- Damage criteria defined in AMM

## Compliance Status
Inspection procedure drafted
